column4: tweets
I forgot how good it felt out here in Florida.  It's so hott here but the weather is beautiful.
Tough loss last night.  Indiana been playing real good lately.
The Knicks have some amazing fans.  They were loud and supportive these last few home games like we were going to the playoffs.  LOVE IT.
Hope everyone has a blessed great day.  Bout to get ready to head to Toronto.  Hope it's not too cool up there.
One more game left.  Great to finish the last home game in the Garden with a win.  Good job fellas.
Just touched down in Miami.  Miss this good weather.  Bout to get some grub then relax.
Let's go Tigers.  Continental got direct TV so I'm able to watch the game.  Hope I can get to the hotel in time to finish the 2nd half.
Doing physicals since 730 am.  Gone get it out the way.  The bed at the hotel is still calling me though.  Oh well.
Thanks tweeps for the prayers and support.  Faith and prayers go a long way.
Morning tweeps.  Great breakfast at the hotel and they had grits.   First time I've had grits anywhere in Miami.
I want to wish everyone in Twitter world a blessed and Happy Thanksgiving.  Eat enough for both of us.  :)
San Francisco what's happening?   Gonna relax then find a nice spot to eat.  Should be plenty to choose from near the hotel.
Rise N Grind Tweeps.  Hump Day.  Thankful, Grateful, and Blessed.  Hope everyone has a great one.  Holla Back.
Another great win.  We are on a roll.  Nothing beats a win.  No matter how you get it.  A win is a win.
I got pretty much every side they had and a large roasted turkey.  I'm greedy I can't lie.
I was starving after the game driving trying to find sumn to eat.  Guess what I ran up on.  Boston Market.  I almost wrecked
Does anybody besides me think Cam Newton gonna get the Heisman hands down?  For real though.
Gotta do better than what I'm doing.  No excuses.  "Those who want to succeed will find a way; those who don't will find an excuse.".
At the office getting it in.  Just got a good workout in.  Weights and got shots up.  Always room for improvement.  So focused.
Milwaukee Bound.  Signing a 10-Day with the Bucks.  LEHGO!!!  Gotta get ready for this cold weather.  BRRRR
What's up tweeps?  Its Monday last day of February.  If it was easy everybody would do it.  Let's get it.
A high Saturday of 34.  Are you serious?  C'Mon Son.
I was going to boycott getting gas today.  Been getting emails and texts ll week.  My gas light just came on.  Sorry guys.
Prayers go out to Japan and all others affected by the disaster.
WOW......Just saw the highlights of the UConn vs. Pitt game.  Never seen a game winning step back and make someone fall at the buzzer.
If I'm not mistaken the earthquake was a magnitude 8.9 which is the largest recorded since seismologists began keeping up with the data.
I ain't gonna lie...if I was Polk I wouldn't pass for the rest of the game.  HEAT CHECK.
Harrison Barnes got his jersey number tonight.  The kid scored a 40 piece against Clemson.  6-8 from 3.  All these games today been good.
Eating at Cubanitas in downtown Milwaukee.  Great Cuban food.  Feels like I'm back in Miami.
LET'S GO TIGERS!!!!!!!!!
LET'S GO......We got ourselves a game.  C'MON FELLAS
It all comes down to this.  Do or Die.  11.7 seconds.  Down one 66-65 with the ball.  C'Mon Tiger Nation.  Let's GO.
5 minutes to go........This game is still in reach.  Need stops.
Where @STH_Designs at?  We headed to your neck of da woods bruh?
Weather is so nice in ATL.  Ahhhhh
Listening to "All Of The Lights (Remix). Bright lights, night lights, head lights, SHHH, no lights but them infrared lights. ~ Wayne
On the bus headed to the arena in ATL.  Big game tonight.  Gotta get this win.  Playoffs in reach.  Time to make a push. Let's Go.
What's happening tweeps?  Hope everyone has a blessed one.  Headed to shoot around listening to some Kanye.
Once again thanks for the warm welcome Blazer fans. I know the Rose Garden will be rocking tonight. Need to beat the Grizz to lock up #6.
What's up tweeps? Its official. I signed with the Blazers for the rest of the season today. Two games left then playoff time. LET'S GET IT
Wanna say what's up to all the Portland fans and thanks for the warm welcome.  Big game tonight against Memphis.  Let's Go.
What's up Tweeps? Last night that jet lag hit me like crazy. It was 10:30 and it felt like 2 or so.  Got a strong 8 hours plus  #AHHHHH

******Yawning wiping crust out eyes****** Can't wait to go back to sleep on the plane. Toooooo early........thanks Sandy.
Prayers go out to D Rose.  Stay strong and stay positive. #tigernation
